    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is a fantastic diamond in the rough, ready for a dedicated owner to give it the mechanical attention it needs to shine again. While it currently requires significant repairs and TLC, it offers a great foundation for anyone looking for a rewarding restoration project at an accessible price!",
